  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Okular</title>

    <para>Okular is a document viewer for KDE. It can view documents of many types 
    including PDF, PostScript, TIFF, Microsoft CHM, DjVu, DVI, XPS and ePub.</para> 

    &lfs71_checked;

